org.block.project.block

Interface BlockType<B extends Block>

  • Type Parameters:
    B - The Blocks class type it is connected with
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NumberBlock.NumberBlockType, SumOperation.SumOperationType

    public interface BlockType<B extends Block>
    The BlockType provides global data between all Blocks it produces. The BlockType is used with the display chooser to produce new blocks with default values
